info.description: This template searches for missing HTTP security headers. The impact of these missing headers can vary.

request:
GET / HTTP/1.1
Host: example.com
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (ZZ; Linux i686; rv:121.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/121.0
Connection: close
Accept: */*
Accept-Language: en
Accept-Encoding: gzip
curl-command: curl -X 'GET' -H 'Accept: */*' -H 'Accept-Language: en' -H 'User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (ZZ; Linux i686; rv:121.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/121.0' 'http://example.com'
